This paper is about building intelligent conversational agents using machine learning, which falls under the category of natural language processing (NLP) and artificial intelligence (AI). Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). Other likely sub-categories include cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.IR (Information Retrieval), and cs.SD (Software Engineering).
